<subSubSection box="[151,888,801,825]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="86.[151,1436,151,825]" box="[151,888,801,825]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">
<emphasis box="[151,271,801,825]" italics="true" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">Etymology</emphasis>
—The name pilulus refers to the hairy SS and the SES.
</paragraph>
